                'description' => '<p>Hotel Orchid is a sophisticated mid-range property whose interior design draws inspiration from the orchid flower — a symbol of refined beauty, rare quality, and graceful elegance. Over 40 varieties of live orchid are cultivated in the hotel\'s greenhouse and displayed throughout the property, creating an atmosphere of natural luxury.</p><p>The hotel is known for its exceptional level of personal service, with a guest-to-staff ratio that allows for a genuinely attentive experience. The in-house Orchid Spa uses orchid-extract treatments developed exclusively for the property, including the signature Himalayan Orchid Facial.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Check-in: 2:00 PM | Check-out: 12:00 PM | Orchid Spa: 9:00 AM – 8:00 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Live orchid display throughout', 'Orchid greenhouse on-site', 'Orchid Spa & treatments', 'Signature Himalayan Orchid Facial', 'High staff-to-guest ratio', 'Luxury rooms', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Air conditioning', 'Premium toiletries', 'Restaurant', 'Laundry & dry cleaning', 'Airport transfer']),
            ],
            'queens-park-hotel' => [
                'description' => '<p>Queens Park Hotel is a characterful 3-star hotel set in a spacious property with a large garden park — an increasingly rare feature in the growing city of Pokhara. The hotel\'s gardens are maintained to an exceptional standard, with manicured lawns, mature trees providing natural shade, and a series of pavilion seating areas ideal for outdoor relaxation.</p><p>The hotel has been a popular choice for wedding receptions and cultural events for decades, thanks to its large event lawn and elegant indoor banquet hall. Leisure guests appreciate the garden\'s tranquillity, the swimming pool, and the helpful in-house travel desk that can arrange any activity in the Annapurna region.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Open 24 hours | Restaurant: 7:00 AM – 10:30 PM | Pool: 7:00 AM – 7:00 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Large garden park', 'Swimming pool', 'Wedding & event lawn', 'Indoor banquet hall', 'Manicured gardens', 'Outdoor pavilions', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Air conditioning', 'Restaurant & bar', 'In-house travel desk', 'Free parking', 'Laundry service']),
            ],
            'raniban-arcade' => [
                'description' => '<p>Raniban Arcade is a distinctive property that takes its name from Raniban — the "Queen\'s Forest" — the lush protected woodland on the ridge above Pokhara. The hotel sits at the forest boundary, offering guests the privilege of direct access to forest trails from the back garden while remaining connected to the Lakeside district below.</p><p>Morning walks through the Raniban forest are a highlight of any stay — the dappled light through the sal trees, the chorus of birds at dawn, and the views of Phewa Lake glimpsed through the canopy are unforgettable. The hotel arranges guided nature walks, meditation in the forest, and forest yoga sessions for interested guests.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Check-in: 1:00 PM | Check-out: 11:00 AM | Restaurant: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Direct Raniban forest access', 'Forest trail from back garden', 'Guided nature walks', 'Forest yoga sessions', 'Forest meditation', 'Bird-watching on-site', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Air conditioning', 'Restaurant', 'Garden seating', 'Laundry service', 'Airport transfer']),
            ],
            'peace-plaza-hotel' => [
                'description' => '<p>Peace Plaza Hotel lives up to its name as a quiet, well-priced property offering genuine peace in the heart of bustling Lakeside. Its leafy courtyard provides a natural sound buffer from the street, and the attentive staff contribute to an atmosphere of calm and quiet efficiency.</p><p>The hotel is particularly popular with solo trekkers and cyclists who appreciate the secure bike storage, knowledgeable travel desk, and the outstanding value breakfast included with each room. The rooftop terrace offers views of both the lake and the green hills to the east.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Check-in: 12:00 PM | Check-out: 11:00 AM | Restaurant: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Courtyard garden', 'Secure bicycle storage', 'Breakfast included', 'Rooftop terrace', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Air conditioning', '24-hour reception', 'Knowledgeable travel desk', 'Safe deposit box', 'Laundry service', 'Daily housekeeping', 'Luggage storage']),
            ],
            'hotel-river-park' => [
                'description' => '<p>Hotel River Park is a peaceful property nestled beside the Seti River, one of Pokhara\'s most dramatic natural features — a milky-white glacial river that disappears underground through dramatic gorges and reappears at the river park just minutes from the hotel. This unique natural setting makes the hotel a base for white-water rafting, gorge exploration, and nature photography.</p><p>The hotel\'s riverside garden is one of Pokhara\'s most tranquil outdoor spaces, with the sound of the river providing a constant natural backdrop. Rafting operators and adventure guides operate from the hotel reception, making it easy to plan an action-packed day from the comfort of your room.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Open 24 hours | Restaurant: 7:00 AM – 10:00 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Seti River location', 'Riverside garden', 'Rafting arrangement on-site', 'Gorge exploration tours', 'Nature photography base', 'Adventure sports centre', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Air conditioning', 'Restaurant', 'Luggage storage', 'Laundry service', 'Airport transfer']),
            ],
            'hotel-mandala' => [
                'description' => '<p>Hotel Mandala draws its identity from the sacred circular mandala motif — a symbol of the universe, wholeness, and the interconnectedness of all things — that recurs throughout the hotel\'s décor, from hand-painted bedroom walls to the circular mosaic at the entrance. The overall effect is meditative and deeply beautiful.</p><p>The hotel is popular with artists, writers, and spiritually-inclined travellers who appreciate the visual richness of the space and the contemplative atmosphere. Regular cultural events include Tibetan Buddhist art workshops, thangka painting demonstrations, and evening readings on Himalayan philosophy. The rooftop meditation platform offers unbroken mountain views.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Check-in: 12:00 PM | Check-out: 11:00 AM | Café & restaurant: 7:00 AM – 9:30 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Mandala-motif décor throughout', 'Rooftop meditation platform', 'Thangka painting workshops', 'Tibetan Buddhist art events', 'Himalayan philosophy evenings', 'Artist-in-residence programme', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Air conditioning', 'Organic café', 'Meditation room', 'Laundry service', 'Airport transfer']),
            ],
            'international-youth-hostel-inn' => [
                'description' => '<p>International Youth Hostel Inn is Pokhara\'s most welcoming hub for backpackers, gap-year travellers, and budget-conscious adventurers from around the world. The hostel has been connecting travellers since its founding and maintains the spirit of the classic youth hostel tradition — affordable, social, and genuinely international.</p><p>The hostel offers dormitory beds, twin rooms, and private doubles, all maintained to a good standard of cleanliness. The communal kitchen allows self-catering, and the outdoor social terrace is a 24-hour gathering point where trekking groups form, travel tips are exchanged, and friendships begin. The friendly staff speak multiple languages and can arrange every activity in the Annapurna region.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => 'Open 24 hours | Kitchen: 6:30 AM – 10:00 PM',
                'features' => $this->features(['Dormitory & private rooms', 'Communal self-catering kitchen', '24-hour social terrace', 'Multilingual staff', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Locker storage in dorms', 'Budget-friendly pricing', 'Trekking group formation', 'ACAP permit advice', 'Luggage storage', 'Laundry service', 'Tour booking available']),
            ],
        ];

        foreach ($hotels as $slug => $data) {
            Business::where('slug', $slug)->where('type', 'hotel')->update($data);
        }

        $this->command->info('Hotel detail seeding complete. ' . count($hotels) . ' hotel records targeted.');
    }

    private function seedRestaurantDetails(): void
