            'the-juicery-cafe' => [
                'description' => '<p>The Juicery Café is Pokhara\'s dedicated health-and-wellness café, a bright, energetic space where cold-pressed juices, smoothie bowls, and plant-based food are the stars. Founded by a nutritionist and a chef who met while teaching at a Pokhara cooking school, the café is driven by a genuine belief in food as medicine.</p><p>The juice bar offers 35 cold-pressed varieties, from immunity boosters packed with ginger and turmeric to post-trek recovery blends with banana, peanut butter, and Himalayan salt. The food menu covers açaí bowls, avocado toasts, raw energy balls, and a rotating daily special. Everything is prepared without refined sugar, artificial additives, or MSG.</p>',
