            'la-viva-restaurant-cafe' => [
                'description' => '<p>La Viva Restaurant & Café brings a Mediterranean warmth and vivacity to Lakeside Pokhara, with a menu that roams the coastlines of Italy, Spain, Greece, and the Middle East without apology. The terrace dining area, strung with terracotta pots, olive trees in planters, and warm amber lighting, is among the most inviting restaurant settings in the city.</p><p>Pizza from a wood-fired oven, handmade pasta with fresh pesto, Greek salad with locally made feta, Spanish-style grilled octopus, and Moroccan-spiced lamb — La Viva pulls off this ambitious range with consistent success. The wine list is one of the most thoughtfully curated in Pokhara, with a genuine effort to represent the regions the menu draws from.</p>',
