            'samrat-tandoori-restaurant' => [
                'description' => '<p>Samrat Tandoori Restaurant has been one of Pokhara\'s most reliable and beloved Indian restaurants for over 15 years. Its clay tandoor ovens, burning with seasoned hardwood since early morning, produce the fragrant naan, succulent kebabs, and tender tikka dishes that have earned Samrat a devoted regular clientele.</p><p>The restaurant excels at the full spectrum of North Indian cuisine: rich butter chicken, silky dal makhani, crispy samosas, and the legendary mixed grill platter that arrives at the table with a theatrical flourish of smoke. The lunch thali offers extraordinary value, with 8–10 dishes for a fixed price that includes unlimited bread.</p>',
