            'pokhara-family-restaurant' => [
                'description' => '<p>Pokhara Family Restaurant is exactly what a family restaurant should be: welcoming, unpretentious, reliably good, and priced so that families can eat without counting coins. Run by a large extended family whose children and grandchildren now help in the kitchen and at tables, the restaurant has served generations of both local and travelling families since 1992.</p><p>The menu covers traditional Nepali and Indian dishes with a few international crowd-pleasers for younger or less adventurous palates. The family dal bhat — enormous portions with four seasonal vegetable dishes, lentils, pickle, and curd — is considered among the best in Lakeside. Children\'s portions and menus are available upon request.</p>',
