            'pokhara-chinese-restaurant' => [
                'description' => '<p>Pokhara Chinese Restaurant is the city\'s most authentic Chinese dining destination — a veteran establishment operated by a family with roots in the Sichuanese and Cantonese culinary traditions. The restaurant does not cater to a generic "Chinese food" expectation but instead serves the real, complex, and occasionally fiery flavours of regional Chinese cooking.</p><p>Signature dishes include mapo tofu with genuine Sichuan peppercorn heat, hand-pulled noodles in bone broth, steamed dim sum on weekend mornings, and a whole-fish preparation that is ordered weeks in advance by regular customers. The restaurant is small, unadorned, and focused entirely on the quality of the food.</p>',
