            'little-big-cafe-pokhara' => [
                'description' => '<p>Little Big Café is Pokhara\'s most delightful contradiction — a tiny venue with enormous ambition, a small menu executed to a standard that punches well above its compact footprint. The café seats only 22 people and the kitchen has space for two, but the quality of what emerges from that kitchen has earned it a reputation that far exceeds its size.</p><p>The concept is simple: a handful of dishes, sourced from the best local producers, prepared with serious culinary skill, and served in a space designed to feel like a friend\'s living room. The coffee is outstanding, the eggs benedict is a Lakeside legend, and the weekend brunch waitlist begins the moment the door opens at 8 AM.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => '8:00 AM – 4:00 PM (Tue to Sun, closed Mondays)',
                'features' => $this->features(['22-seat intimate café', 'Specialty coffee', 'Eggs Benedict legend', 'Weekend brunch waitlist', 'Locally sourced produce', 'Friend\'s living room atmosphere', 'Small but perfectly executed menu', 'Natural light space', 'Free Wi-Fi', 'Cash only']),
