            'nirvana-terrace-bar-lounge' => [
                'description' => '<p>Nirvana Terrace Bar & Lounge is Pokhara\'s most atmospheric evening venue — a rooftop terrace bar positioned above the Lakeside rooftops, where the Annapurna range forms the backdrop to every cocktail and conversation. The name references both the Buddhist concept of ultimate peace and the feeling guests consistently describe when they first take in the view.</p><p>The cocktail programme is the finest in Lakeside, led by a trained mixologist who creates seasonal menus using local herbs, mountain honey, Himalayan salt, and Nepali spirits. The lounge serves sophisticated bar snacks — bruschetta, cheese boards, charcuterie — designed to complement rather than overshadow the drinks. Live acoustic performances most evenings from 7 PM.</p>',
