            'daddys-kitchen' => [
                'description' => '<p>Daddy\'s Kitchen is a homestyle Nepali and Indian restaurant where the owner-chef — universally known as "Daddy" — has been cooking for travellers and locals with the generous spirit of a family patriarch since 1999. The restaurant is beloved for its enormous portions, house-made pickles, and the famous "Daddy\'s Special" — a daily changing curry prepared from whatever looks best at the morning market.</p><p>The dhido (buckwheat porridge) with gundruk (fermented greens) and Daddy\'s chicken curry are the dishes that keep regulars coming back year after year. Every table gets a complimentary bowl of house-made yoghurt to start and a small sweet to finish — gestures of hospitality that reflect the owner\'s character.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => '7:30 AM – 10:00 PM (open daily)',
