            ],
            'krazy-gecko' => [
                'description' => '<p>Krazy Gecko is a Lakeside institution with a personality as big and colourful as its name — a loud, fun, unpretentious bar and restaurant that has been hosting celebrations, reunions, and spontaneous adventures since the early 2000s. The gecko motif appears throughout the décor in dozens of forms, from painted murals to ceramic figurines to the neon sign that has become one of Lakeside\'s most recognisable landmarks.</p><p>The food menu covers the bases that hungry, happy travellers need: good burgers, loaded nachos, fish and chips, pasta, and an extensive pizza menu. The bar stocks everything from local Everest beer to premium spirits, and the weekly quiz night (Wednesday, 7 PM) draws the best-informed crowd in Pokhara.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => '10:00 AM – midnight (open daily) | Quiz night: Wednesdays 7:00 PM',
