            'almonds-cafe-restaurant' => [
                'description' => '<p>Almond\'s Café & Restaurant is a calm, light-filled café that uses the almond as a culinary metaphor for its philosophy — something simple, nutritious, and endlessly versatile. The café specialises in healthy, whole-food cooking with an international range that effortlessly spans breakfast, lunch, and dinner without losing coherence or quality.</p><p>Almond granola bowls, almond-milk lattes, almond pesto pasta, and almond-crusted fish are examples of how the café builds signature dishes around its namesake ingredient. Beyond the almond theme, the menu offers a broad range of plant-based and omnivore options, all prepared with fresh local ingredients and genuine care.</p>',
