            'the-lemon-tree-restaurant' => [
                'description' => '<p>The Lemon Tree Restaurant is a bright, citrus-coloured café-restaurant that has been one of the most consistently excellent dining spots in Lakeside for over a decade. Its lemon tree motif — representing freshness, sourness, and the unexpected burst of flavour that lifts any dish — informs a menu built around bold, clean flavours and quality ingredients.</p><p>The restaurant excels at breakfast (the lemon ricotta pancakes have a devoted following), lunch (the lemon-herb chicken wrap is a perennial bestseller), and dinner (the lemon curd tart with house cream is a must-order dessert). The terrace, shaded by a genuine lemon tree in a large pot, is among the most sought-after seats in Lakeside.</p>',
