            'rosemary-kitchen' => [
                'description' => '<p>Rosemary Kitchen is a long-standing Lakeside favourite that draws its name and culinary identity from the fragrant herb that runs through so many of its dishes. The restaurant combines reliable European comfort food with a warm, herb-garden aesthetic — rosemary wreaths on the walls, potted herbs on every table, and the scent of wood-roasted garlic and rosemary drifting from the kitchen throughout service.</p><p>Rosemary roast chicken, lamb with rosemary and lemon, rosemary flatbread with olive oil, and rosemary panna cotta are among the signature dishes that have made this restaurant a weekly ritual for Pokhara\'s expatriate community. The wine list is concise but carefully chosen, with the emphasis on value and food compatibility.</p>',
                'opening_hours' => '11:00 AM – 10:30 PM (open daily)',
